'Lnc'-ing Wnt in female reproductive cancers: therapeutic potential of long 
non-coding RNAs in Wnt signalling.

Ong MS(1), Cai W(2)(3), Yuan Y(3), Leong HC(2)(3), Tan TZ(3), Mohammad A(3), You 
ML(3), Arfuso F(4), Goh BC(2)(3)(5)(6), Warrier S(7)(8), Sethi G(2)(8), 
