(6)Institute of Biological, Environmental and Rural Sciences, Aberystwyth 
University, Aberystwyth, SY23 3EB, United Kingdom. naf4@aber.ac.uk.
(7)Integrative Biomedical Informatics Group, GRIB, IMIM, Department of 
Experimental and Life Sciences, Universitat Pompeu Fabra, Barcelona, 08003, 
Catalonia, Spain. laura.furlong@upf.edu.
(8)Structural Bioinformatics Group, GRIB, IMIM, Department of Experimental and 
